    "English": "The brain stem of a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">brood mother</span>, pulled from its malignant corpse.<br><br>This is a valuable trophy, signifying victory in the quest to purge the infestations of the vile brood. Turn it over to an envoy of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Mercenaries Guild</span> to mark your triumph.",
